          "content": "**Key Design Decisions**\n\n**Agent:** ReAct pattern with `create_react_agent` for dynamic tool selection\n\n**Memory:** `ConversationBufferMemory` persists chat history and 2 user preferences (favorite team, tournament)\n\n**LLMs:** 3 separate GPT-3.5-turbo instances with different temperatures:\n- Agent: temp=0.0 (deterministic)\n- Synthesis: temp=0.3 (creative)\n- Prediction: temp=0.2 (balanced)\n\n**Max iterations:** 8 per query",
