        {
          "id": "e4",
          "type": "code",
          "language": "python",
          "content": "# 1. Load World Cup CSV with LangChain CSVLoader\nloader = CSVLoader(file_path=wc_csv_path)\ndocuments = loader.load()           # 964 documents\n\n# 2. Split into chunks\ntext_splitter = RecursiveCharacterTextSplitter(\n    chunk_size=500, chunk_overlap=50\n)\nsplit_docs = text_splitter.split_documents(documents)\n\n# 3. Build FAISS vector store\nembeddings = OpenAIEmbeddings()\nvectorstore = FAISS.from_documents(split_docs, embeddings)\nretriever = vectorstore.as_retriever(search_kwargs={\"k\": 8})",
          "position": { "x": 60, "y": 100 },
          "size": { "w": 500, "h": 300 },
          "style": {
            "theme": "github-light",
            "fontSize": 13,
            "borderRadius": 8,
            "highlightLines": [3, 9, 13]
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "e5",
          "type": "text",
          "content": "**Pipeline Flow**\n\n**CSVLoader** reads each CSV row as a LangChain `Document`\n\n**RecursiveCharacterTextSplitter** chunks documents (500 chars, 50 overlap)\n\n**OpenAIEmbeddings** generates vector representations\n\n**FAISS** stores 964 vectors for fast similarity search\n\n**Retriever** returns top-8 relevant documents per query",
          "position": { "x": 580, "y": 100 },
          "size": { "w": 350, "h": 280 },
          "style": { "fontSize": 16, "color": "#334155", "lineHeight": 1.7 }
